<h2>
    Sustainable and Ethical Fishing Practices
</h2>
<p>
    Respecting the ecosystem is essential. Chum salmon play a critical role in local river systems by delivering nutrients as they spawn and die. Here’s how to fish ethically:
</p>
<ul>
